          "title": "Coin Change Greedy Trap",
          "body": "Greedy fails for coins=[1,3,4] amount=6: greedy gives 4+1+1=3 coins, but DP gives 3+3=2 coins. Always test greedy before assuming it works — use DP when unsure."
