                'Safexpress (India logistics): Needed to win a Bollywood film distribution deal. They delivered Harry Potter books to EVERY bookstore in India on release day \u2014 every book, 8 AM, no leaks. That ONE delivery won the deal. The prospect didn\'t need to hear about Safexpress\'s infrastructure. The Harry Potter delivery was a Sinatra Test: "If they can do THAT, they can do anything."',
                'Won a major Bollywood distribution deal with ONE credential demonstration',
